                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> A target creature within 30 feet must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:25] save or gain the effects of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Cursed Metamorphosis], being polymorphed into a pig whose girth is determined by the target's wealth. After 24 hours, the target can end this effect using a Dismiss action, at which point the yeongno becomes aware that the effect has ended. A yeongno can use Fortune's Favor only if no targets are currently under its effects.</p>"
