                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The target is carrying at least 100 gp worth of precious metals</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The yeongno crushes a creature it can see with the weight of their wealth. Apparitions of gold coins approximating the wealth of the target materialize and pummel the target from all sides. The target attempts a @Check[will|dc:25] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes @Damage[3d6[persistent,mental]] damage and is slowed 1 as long as the damage continues. The effect immediately ends if they're carrying less than 100 gp worth of precious metals.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, except any flat checks to remove the persistent damage automatically fail.</p>"
